1. App records your voice
2. App sends it to our server
3. Our server redirects your voice to OpenAI Whisper API
4. Our server send the recognised text back to you
5. Right after the recognition we remove your voice from our server. 
Though we have access to your voice recording on our server during the recognition, we promise not to listen to it.
Also you can check OpenAI API privacy policy: https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy
